channel.title: How to Set Rune-Legacy Server online (Anti-leech fixed, Ports are open.)
channel.description:
Hey, I Fixed the Rune-Legacy Anti-leech a while ago, and made the client connect to the right GUi. And i am not just "Leeching" I added my own stuff to it, and deleted a shitload of stuff. I just want to use it as a base because i like the Pking.
For a reason i can't get it online. The problem aint the portforwarding, cua all the port testers says "Open" And for a double check i just putted a random PI source online to test it. (Did work)
What i tryed to get it online:
Portforwarding ofcourse Changed the Port in server.java (Server sided to 5555) (was 1 spot) Changed the port in Client.java (client sided to 5555) I found 2 spots 1 that sayd 43594 and 43595, changed them Both. Changed the IP in Client.java (client sided To my No-ip) I found 2 Spots near ea other.
But i just wont get online, Plz can someone help me out with this. Because this isn't the Anti-Leech there is no reason to say, "Fuck off ur not worth it" Just help me out with this
Are there any more spots i need to edit stuff? or Other files?? Plz tell me
I willl thank/Repp
And again, Please help me i worked hard on my new minigame i want to test it.
